            "image_overlay_opacity": 66,
            "heading": "<strong>Our Story</strong>",
            "heading_size": "h3",
            "subheading": "",
            "description": "<p>Proferlo is an Australian furniture brand that actually owns its factory, so good design reaches you without the middleman markup. Built for first homes, rentals and fresh starts — and shipped Australia-wide.</p>",
